snippet.title: onaretrotip
snippet.description:
Hi, guys. Thanks for checking out my channel. I'm Pete, and as you've probably guessed, I'm on a retro tip!

This channel is devoted to all things retro gaming, including...

- Developer Spotlight, taking a look at the history and games of iconic developers.
- Cancelled Games, looking at unreleased retro games for various systems.
- Arcade Exclusives, where we look at some of the arcade-only games from a developer.
- Essential DOS Games, delving into some of the must-play DOS games, genre by genre.
- In da House, where I visit other collectors' homes.

And also top ten lists, collection updates, and showing new games for retro systems.
